Interface ResultSetIterable<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Iterable<T>

    public interface ResultSetIterable<T>
extends Iterable<T>, AutoCloseable
    Iterable ResultSet. Needs to be closeable, because allowing manual iteration means it's impossible to know when to close the ResultSet and Connection.
